descriptionHtml:
[CENTER][I][COLOR=#8DB3E2][FONT=Courier][B][SIZE=7][U]Eastmarch Redone[/U][/SIZE][/B][/FONT][/COLOR][/I]


[FONT=Verdana][B][COLOR=#CCC1D9][SIZE=3]Made this mod because i didnt like the green flora in the volcanic area like bushes and trees so i removed them in that area did also changed the texture on the ground so it would fit the changes to where the green flora were.[/FONT][/B][/COLOR][/SIZE]

[FONT=Verdana][B][COLOR=#CCC1D9][SIZE=3]If you like it dont forget to endorse and ofc comment thank you![/SIZE][/COLOR][/B][/FONT]
[COLOR=#7F7F7F][SIZE=7][I][B]___________________________________[/B][/I][/SIZE][/COLOR][/COLOR]

[COLOR=#8DB3E2][SIZE=5][B][FONT=Courier][U]Compatibility and Requirements[/U][/FONT][/B][/SIZE]
[/COLOR]

[FONT=Verdana][B][COLOR=#CCC1D9][SIZE=3]Updated Skyrim to latest is recommended.
The mod is not compatible with anything that modifies the same Cell/Area.[/SIZE][/COLOR][/B][/FONT]
